visa_letter_request.body:
Dear HR Team,

I am writing to request a visa support letter for my upcoming travel.

Travel Details:
- Destination: {destination}
- Purpose: {purpose}
- Travel Dates: {travelDates}

I would appreciate if you could provide the letter at your earliest convenience.

Please let me know if you need any additional information.

Thank you,
{fullName}
{jobTitle}
{companyName}

